{"tid":1917153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇：每個國家都應像中國一樣 才能使疫情緩解","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T22:14:52.000Z","uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"826e146971885bd0278b902f83a260438a887740","tid":1917153,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"袁國勇亦在訪問中說，當50多個國家都出現疫情，已是全球大爆發。他認為每個國家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都應像中國一樣做足防疫</span>，才能使疫情緩解，否則這波疫情隨時比2003年的SARS更嚴重。他認為，現時意大利、韓國等地，甚至將來美國都可能「反輸入」病例到中國，故疫情防控不可放鬆，亦要考慮邊境管制，從疫區來的人須隔離14日，否則前功盡廢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1x4FmhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1x4FmhK.jpg&h=1d1712e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200307/s00001/1583519656137/%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%95%E7%9F%A5%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%88%86%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200307%2Fs00001%2F1583519656137%2F%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587-%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2595%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=cf0767d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200307%2Fs00001%2F1583519656137%2F%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587-%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2595%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B&h=39fea5c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpa